Merge pull request #29 from Sydney-Informatics-Hub/glnexus-jemalloc

Change glnexus container

Change glnexus container

The container does not contain jemalloc, which is recommended by GLnexus developes in order to improve performance at high thread counts. 
The updated container does include jemalloc (version 5.2.1-0-gea6b3e973b477b8061e0076bb257dbd7f3faa756)
